'''多明尼克·愛德華·庫柏'''（{{lang-en|Dominic Edward Cooper}}，{{bd|1978年|6月2日}}）<ref name=rovi>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/303046/Dominic-Cooper/biography | title = Dominic Cooper | first = Nathan | last = Southern | publisher = [[All_Media_Guide|All Media Guide]] / [[Rovi|Rovi]] via ''The New York Times'' | accessdate = 2014-05-10 | archive-date = 2016-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306205442/http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/303046/Dominic-Cooper/biography | dead-url = no }}</ref>是一位[[英國|英國]]男演員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/feb/11/dominic-cooper-saddam-devils-double |title=Dominic Cooper leaves Mamma Mia! far behind to play Saddam's son |publisher=The Guardian |date=2014-03-13 |accessdate=2014-05-09 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125061357/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/feb/11/dominic-cooper-saddam-devils-double |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他較著名的是在[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]的電影《[[美國隊長_(電影)|美國隊長]]》（2011年）、短片《[[卡特探員_(電影)|卡特探員]]》（2013年）電視劇《[[卡特探員|卡特探員]]》（2015年至2016年）中飾演青年時期[[霍華·史塔克|霍華·史塔克]]。

其他參演過的著名作品如《[[戀愛學分|戀愛學分]]》（2006年）、《[[公爵夫人_(電影)|公爵夫人]]》（2008年）、《[[媽媽咪呀！_(電影)|媽媽咪呀！]]》（2008年）、《[[魔鬼替身|魔鬼替身]]》（2011年）和《[[德古拉：永咒傳奇|德古拉：永咒傳奇]]》（2014年）。

2016年，庫柏於電影《[[魔獸：崛起|魔獸：崛起]]》飾演暴風城國王萊茵，並於[[DC漫畫|DC漫畫]]改編電視劇《[[傳教士_(電視劇)|傳教士]]》中主演{{link-en|傑西·卡斯特|Jesse Custer}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/04/17/preacher-dominic-cooper-is-jesse-custer|title=Preacher: Dominic Cooper is Jesse Custer|publisher=IGN|last=Fowler|first=Matt|date=April 17, 2015|accessdate=September 10, 2015|archive-date=2019-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224104532/https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/04/17/preacher-dominic-cooper-is-jesse-custer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==早期生活==
庫柏出生於[[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[格林尼治|格林尼治]]<ref>{{cite news |first=James |last=Mottram |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/features/interview-dominic-cooper--i-nearly-broke-ronnie-woods-shoulder-8877311.html |title=Interview: Dominic Cooper - 'I nearly broke Ronnie Wood's shoulder' |publisher=The Independent |date=2013-10-14 |accessdate=2014-05-09 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925035056/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/features/interview-dominic-cooper--i-nearly-broke-ronnie-woods-shoulder-8877311.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。為托兒所老師朱莉（Julie，娘家姓為Heron）與拍賣師布萊恩·庫柏（Brian Cooper）的兒子<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/super-cooper-dominic-coopers-hollywood-education-6797414.html | title = Super Cooper: Dominic Cooper's Hollywood education | first = Lina | last = Das | date = 8 October 2009 | work = [[London_Evening_Standard|London Evening Standard]] | quote = There are few 31-year-old actors who can claim... | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | archive-date = 2020-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200824073822/https://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/super-cooper-dominic-coopers-hollywood-education-6797414.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ref12">{{cite news|last=Hardy|first=Rebecca|title=Secrets of the new Mr Darcy: Rising star Dominic Cooper|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|location=UK|date=11 January 2008|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-507470/Secrets-new-Mr-Darcy-Rising-star-Dominic-Cooper.html|accessdate=20 July 2008|quote=...the 29-year-old...|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20080604012017/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-507470/Secrets-new-Mr-Darcy-Rising-star-Dominic-Cooper.html|archivedate=2008-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Broadway.com">{{cite web | url= http://www.broadway.com/gen/Buzz_Story.aspx?ci=527884 | title= Dominic Cooper, Fresh Face | date= 26 September 2007 | accessdate= 17 October 2006 | first= Katie | last= Riegel | publisher= Broadway.com | quote= Age: 27 | archivedate= 2007-09-26 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070926212559/http://www.broadway.com/gen/Buzz_Story.aspx?ci=527884 | dead-url= no }}</ref>。他的母親的曾祖父{{link-en|愛德華·湯瑪斯·赫倫|Edward Thomas Heron}}是電影愛好者，他曾出版《{{link-en|Kinematograph周刊|Kinematograph Weekly}}》。

庫柏就讀了{{link-en|約翰鮑爾小學|John Ball Primary School}}其次是附近的{{link-en|湯瑪斯塔利斯學校|Thomas Tallis School}}，後於2000年從[[倫敦音樂與戲劇藝術學院|倫敦音樂與戲劇藝術學院]]畢業。

==個人生活==
自2010年起，他開始與女演員[[露絲·奈嘉|露絲·奈嘉]]交往並同居住[[倫敦|倫敦]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/how-oscartipped-ruth-neggas-star-has-finally-ascended-34730596.html|title=How Oscar-tipped Ruth Negga's star has finally ascended...|date=23 May 2016|last=Notaro|first=Vicki|accessdate=23 May 2016|work=[[Irish_Independent|Irish Independent]]|archive-date=2018-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728071409/https://www.independent.ie/entertainment/how-oscartipped-ruth-neggas-star-has-finally-ascended-34730596.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.ie/style/celebrity/celebrity-news/irish-actress-ruth-negga-and-dominic-cooper-make-rare-public-appearance-at-warcraft-premiere-34783050.html|title=Irish actress Ruth Negga and Dominic Cooper make rare public appearance at Warcraft premiere|date=8 June 2016|last=McBride|first=Caitlin|accessdate=9 June 2016|work=[[Irish_Independent|Irish Independent]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108101832/https://www.independent.ie/style/celebrity/celebrity-news/irish-actress-ruth-negga-and-dominic-cooper-make-rare-public-appearance-at-warcraft-premiere-34783050.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。交往六年後，據悉，兩人已分手，但他們仍是好友關係。

